.DS_Store

# Ephemeral working set: gitignored — the durable record lives in the spec
# (with its `## Execution`), findings/, decisions/, and status.md. Each dir keeps its README.
# Audit-trail opt-in: comment out the two reviews/ lines to commit review packets instead.
intake/*
tasks/*
reviews/*
!intake/README.md
!tasks/README.md
!reviews/README.md
